# No Go Binaries in Git

- **Do not stage or commit** any Go binary produced by `go build` (e.g. `server`, `myapp`, `cmd/foo/foo`, or any `*.exe`). These are local build artifacts.
- Ensure such paths are listed in the project’s **.gitignore**. When committing, ensure no Go binaries are included in the diff.
